On most days,
Twitter is 
Shouting in void

The voice passes
Unnoticed, unheard
Into the great abyss, 
Fleeting
and soon forgotten. 

In the process
I'm more myself.

Uncensored, untamed
Unintelligent even, 
But mostly liberated.
